<p>Here you will find a complete library of online video tutorials. Each one is a few minutes long and walks you through a specific topic.  Whether you're just getting started or you want help working with a specific area, you'll find the material you need here.  We recommend you start in the Getting Started section and work through those videos in order first, then explore the Sample Projects and other topics.</p>
<p></p>
<p>If you have trouble viewing the videos, check the Read Me file for help. You can also order these videos inexpensively on CD, which may be necessary if you have a slow connection.</p>
<p></p>
<p>You can access all the basic topics in this library free.  To access the advanced and more in-depth topics, you need to purchase a separate video tutorials license (included free with Studio or Enterprise).</p>
<p></p>
<p><font color="#000000">Each video has a star rating which gives an indictation of that video's complexity. The ratings range from one star (easy) to three stars (advanced).</font></p>
<p></p>
<p>Be sure to check back regularly, we'll be adding more Advanced Tutorials over the next few weeks.</p>